4^{th}
\cos(\alpha) = \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{5}}, \sin(-\alpha) = -\dfrac{2}{\sqrt{5}} , p = -\dfrac{-3}{\sqrt{5}} = \dfrac{3}{\sqrt{5}}
\alpha \approx 1.10714871779409 ~\mbox{radians}~ \approx 63.434948822922 {}^{\circ}
